TITLE: Creating Basic Panel in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add a basic panel using the Dockview API with a unique ID and component specification. Includes optional inactive flag to prevent automatic activation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/docs/core/panels/add.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
