TITLE: Maximizing Groups with DockviewPanelApi in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the DockviewPanelApi to maximize groups, check maximization status, and exit maximized state. This API provides methods specific to a panel for maximizing its group, checking if it's maximized, and exiting maximized state if applicable.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/docs/core/groups/maxmizedGroups.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const api: DockviewPanelApi;

// maximize the group
api.maximize();

// is this group maximized (if another group is maximized this method will still return false)
const result: boolean = api.isMaxmized();

// exit only if this group is maximzied (if another group is maxmized this has no affect)
api.exitMaximized();
```

