TITLE: Maximizing Groups with DockviewApi in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to maximize groups, check maximization status, and exit maximized state using the DockviewApi. It includes methods for maximizing a specific group, checking if a group is maximized, exiting maximized state, and checking if any group is maximized.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/docs/core/groups/maxmizedGroups.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const api: DockviewApi;

// maximize a specified group
api.maxmimizeGroup(group);

// check whether a specific group is maximized
const result: boolean = api.isMaximizedGroup(group);

// if there is any maximized group exit the maximized state
exitMaximizedGroup();

// is there a maximized group
const result: boolean = hasMaximizedGroup();
```

