TITLE: Panel and Group Resizing in Dockview using TypeScript/React
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates two approaches to resize panels in Dockview: directly using panel API or through the group API. The code shows how to set specific height and width dimensions for panels, with either method achieving the same result.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/docs/core/groups/resizing.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
// it's mandatory to provide either a height or a width, providing both is optional
props.api.setSize({
    height: 100,
    width: 200,
});

// you could also resize the panels group, although not recommended it achieved the same result
props.api.group.api.setSize({
    height: 100,
    width: 200,
});
```

