TITLE: Naive Split View Resizing Algorithm in Pseudocode
DESCRIPTION: This pseudocode presents a basic algorithm for resizing views in a split view control. It iterates through views to the left of the dragged sash, adjusting their sizes based on the remaining delta while respecting minimum and maximum size constraints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/src/misc/math/math.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Pseudocode
CODE:
```
remaining = 
for (j = i; j >= 0; i--) do
    Vnextj = Min(Vmaxj, Max(Vminj, Vj + remaining))
    Vj = Vnextj - Vj
    remaining = remaining - Vj
    Vj = Vnextj
```

