TITLE: Creating HTML Structure for DockView Landing Page
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet defines the structure of the DockView landing page. It includes metadata, external resource links, and content sections for project information and documentation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mathuo/dockview/blob/master/packages/docs/docs/index.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: HTML
CODE:
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DockView</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="#documentation">Documentation</a></li>
                <li><a href="#github">GitHub</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <h1>DockView</h1>
            <p>A flexible docking system for web applications</p>
        </section>

        <section id="features">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Customizable layouts</li>
                <li>Drag and drop functionality</li>
                <li>Resizable panels</li>
                <li>Easy integration with existing projects</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="documentation">
            <h2>Documentation</h2>
            <p>Check out our comprehensive documentation to get started with DockView:</p>
            <a href="docs/index.html" class="btn">View Documentation</a>
        </section>

        <section id="github">
            <h2>GitHub</h2>
            <p>DockView is open-source! Contribute to the project on GitHub:</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/mathuo/dockview" class="btn"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub Repository</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 DockView. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

